  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chorizo and cook for 3-4 minutes, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the mustard seeds and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the apple cider vinegar and stir to deglaze the pan.",
    "Add the potatoes and cook for 5-6 minutes, or until they are tender.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
